  "decision_conditions": [
    "The development to which this permission relates will be for a temporary time until May 2025 where the use and the hereby agreed temporary arrangements (including parking, zebra crossing etc) shall revert back to the details of the original Beam Park Masterplan under reference P1242.17 (as amended under any subsequent S73 or S96A applications).",
    "Reason:-To comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.",
